{"tid":332014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃其他地區附加賽名額賽決賽－李海娜vs林詩枝","createTime":"2017-07-22T16:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T14:00:14.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"416826c12dae0c4c0a7dfe5033ae988351e2768d","tid":332014,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃其他地區附加賽名額賽決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-23 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/T6mGxcL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FT6mGxcL.png&h=c04ef065&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nNFpF39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnNFpF39.png&h=d1728cc3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qdKYOI7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqdKYOI7.png&h=8719e985&s={SIZE}\" />李海娜 vs 林詩枝<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/i2eVNeb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi2eVNeb.png&h=8fa43878&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本帖發起後22小時內以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"f89ccbaed8f419d1866e6d6daa739ff4d67bb35f","tid":332014,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97ccacbf844ee